title: Ep 2087 - Sodhis Wife Allows Him To Attend Party
shortDesc: Sodhi's wife allows him to attend the party organized by their neighbours. Jethalal calls Bagha and asks him to bring parcel from Sinha's house.

title: Ep 2088 - Bawri Comes To Jethalals House
shortDesc: Bawri brings the wine bottle to Jethalal's house. Jethalal tells Champaklal that the bottle is of an imported perfume.

title: Ep 2089 - Daya And Friends Plan A Mocktail Party
shortDesc: Jethalal tells Bawri that she should have given his parcel to Bagha. Daya and her neighbours decide to organize a cocktail party.

title: Ep 2090 -Jethalal And Friends Gather For Party
shortDesc: Sodhi meets Jethalal and tells him that all his friends are waiting for him in Popatlal's house. Jethalal and his neighbours gather to celebrate a party.

title: Ep 2091 - France Ki Bottle
shortDesc: Jethalal and his friends consume an alcoholic drink brought from France. They soon learn that the drink is poisonous and may cause harm to their health.

title: Ep 2092 - Daya Ka Surprise
shortDesc: Jethalal tells his friends that the wine they had consumed is poisonous. A few ambulances enter Gokuldham society. Daya tells Jethalal and his friends that they need not go to hospital.

title: Ep 2093 -  Chalu Pandey Comes To Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Inspector Chalu Pandey comes to Gokuldham Society and meets Jethalal and his neighbours. He asks them as to why they called ambulances to Gokuldham Society.

title: Ep 2094 - Mr. Sinha Comes To Jethalals House
shortDesc: Champaklal asks Jethalal to give him the perfume bought from France. Mr. Sinha comes to Jethalal's house. He brings a gift for Jethalal.

title: Ep 2095 -  Jethalal Ka Lucky Bangle
shortDesc: Bagha tells Jethalal that Singhania Group of Hotels wish to give them a big order of electronic items. Jethalal heads towards his shop to confirm the order.

title: Ep 2096 -  Ghanchakkar Steals Jethalals Lucky Bangle
shortDesc: Popatlal brings Jethalal to a tea stall. An old man steals the lucky bangle from Jethalal. Later, Jethalal comes to his shop and shares the experience with Natwarlal and Bagha.

title: Ep 2097 -  Manmoji Comes To Jethalals Shop
shortDesc: Manhar Manmoji comes to Jethalal's shop. He tells Bagha and Natwarlal that he is the owner of the shop. He also ends up selling an electronic item to a customer.

title: Ep 2098 -  Manhar Manmoji Ka Aatank
shortDesc: Jethalal informs Chalu Pande that Manhar Manmoji has entered into his shop. He request the police to arrest Manhar at the earliest. Rajkumar Singhania comes to Jethalal's shop.

title: Ep 2100 -  Jethalal Brings Manhar To Gokuldham Society
shortDesc: Jethalal brings Manhar Manmoji to Gokuldham Society. Manhar rides Atmaram Bhide's scooter.

title: Ep 2101 - Manhar Manmoji In Jethalals House
shortDesc:
Daya informs Champaklal that Manhar Manmoji is out of his mind. Two news-reporters come to Jethalal’s house to interview Manhar Manmoji.

title: Ep 2102 - Manhars Son Comes To Jethalals House
shortDesc:
Samir comes to Jethalal’s house and meets his father. Manhar Manmoji informs his son that he will continue to stay in Jethalal’s house.
